The paper deals with font selection and retrieval using a large-scale dataset and a novel generative feature learning algorithm. The use of font images and attention mechanisms suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) techniques. The problem of tag-based retrieval also suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as possible sub-categories.
